(14, 115, 'Desain Komunikasi Visual', 'desain-komunikasi-visual', '<p>Wujudkan impian kamu untuk memasuki Kreatif Digital masa kini, di Program Studi:<strong>S1 DESAIN KOMUNIKASI VISUAL (DKV)</strong>dengan Konsentrasi:</p>\r\n<p><strong>GAME DEVELOPMENT (S1 DESAIN KOMUNIKASI VISUAL)</strong><br />Multimedia Art Director, Character Designer, Enviroment Designer, Concept Artist, Designer UI Junior</p>\r\n<p><strong>ANIMATION (S1 DESAIN KOMUNIKASI VISUAL)</strong><br />2D Animation Development Artist, 3D Animation Development Artist, Puppeter Development Artist, Character Designer Artist, Animation Conceptor</p>\r\n<p><strong>GRAPHIC DESIGN (S1 DESAIN KOMUNIKASI VISUAL)</strong><br />Junior Designer, User Interface Designer, Illustrator Junior, Junior Typeface Designer</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-417 size-full\" src=\"http://infopmb.budiluhur.ac.id/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Fikom-Universitas-Budi-Luhur-2020-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"903\" height=\"1280\" data-pagespeed-url-hash=\"2004837011\" /></p>', '', 1, 2, '2023-04-07 13:33:49', 189, '', '2023-04-07 13:33:49', 189, NULL, NULL, '2023-04-07 13:33:49', NULL, '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":\"\",\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":\"\",\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":\"\",\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"