(30, 'com_content.article.12', '', '2023-04-07 13:32:21', 189, 5209, '6e6c3657e3d161d58d6f35b1690cb868fb1c89ae', '{\"id\":12,\"asset_id\":113,\"title\":\"Magister Ilmu Komunikasi\",\"alias\":\"magister-ilmu-komunikasi\",\"introtext\":\"<p><strong>PROGRAM STUDI MAGISTER ILMU KOMUNIKASI<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>UNIVERSITAS BUDI LUHUR<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>\\u00a0<\\/strong><strong>\\u00a0<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong><em>Corporate Public Relations<\\/em><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Dalam profesi seorang\\u00a0<em>Corporate PR<\\/em>\\u00a0selain harus terampil menyampaikan presentasi lisan, membuat\\u00a0<em>Press Release<\\/em>, mampu menjalin relasi dengan publik, juga harus mahir merancang strategi komunikasi perusahaan yang baik dan terencana. Saat ini, bidang ke-PR-an semakin memperluas peranannya, dengan telah memasuki wilayah Marketing dan juga\\u00a0<em>Corporate Public Relations<\\/em>.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Peluang karir<em>\\u00a0Corporate Public Relations :<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Praktisi Corporate PR, Dosen,\\u00a0<em>PR Marketing, Communication Director, Speech, Writers, Media Relations Manager, Community Relation Manager, Public Affairs<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Dengan kurikulum inti<em>\\u00a0:<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><em>Corporate Public Relations, Marketing Public Relations<\\/em>\\u00a0dan\\u00a0<em>CSR<\\/em>,\\u00a0<em>Crisis Management<\\/em>,\\u00a0<em>Planning<\\/em>\\u00a0and\\u00a0<em>Evaluations of Public Relations<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>\\u00a0<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong><em>Marketing Communications<\\/em><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Profesi Praktisi\\u00a0<em>Marketing Communication<\\/em>\\u00a0adalah profesi yang memiliki teknik untuk menyiapkan dan mendapatkan produk (barang atau jasa) yang baik dengan kualitas yang baik didalam situasi dan tempat yang baik dan mendapatkan keuntungan dalam sebuah penjualan \\/ kegiatan. Oleh karena itu,\\u00a0<em>Marketing<\\/em>\\u00a0bukan hanya sekedar sebuah tugas untuk menjual produk, namun\\u00a0<em>Marketing<\\/em>\\u00a0lebih mengarah kepada apa yang akan dijual, bagaimana cara menjualnya dan dimana tempat produk tersebut akan dijual.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Peluang karier<em>\\u00a0Marketing Communications :<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Praktisi Markom, Dosen,\\u00a0<em>PR Officer, PR Executive, PR Counselor, PR Manager, Press Relations Officer, Corporate Communication Head, Marketing Communication Manager, VIP External Affair, Investor Relations Manager, Corporate Secretary, Publisher<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Dengan kurikulum inti<em>\\u00a0:<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><em>Marketing Communications Multikultural, Integrated Marketing Communications, Digital Marketing Communications, Brand Equity<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Media Industry Communications<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Komunikasi Industri Media\\u00a0 Magister Ilmu Komunikasi Universitas Budi Luhur menggabungkan pemikiran analitis dan kreatif. dimana Konsentrasi ini menyiapkan mahasiswa untuk menguasai konsep dan teori dalam bidang pengetahuan spesialis dan mendalam \\u00a0mengenai pengelolaan komunikasi industri media. Selain itu mahasiswa Konsentrasi ini diajarkan tentang bagaimana mengelola kelebihan, kelemahan, peluang dan ancaman dalam proses penyelenggaraan lembaga dan kegiatan jurnalistik industri media komunikasi.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><em>Peluang karier\\u00a0<\\/em>Komunikasi Industri Media<em>\\u00a0:<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Dosen, Pemimpin Media, Manajer Produksi dan Komunikasi Pemasaran Media, Konsultan Media, Produser Program TV dan Radio,\\u00a0<em>Advertising Manager<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><em>Dengan kurikulum inti :<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><em>Integrated Marketing Communications, Media Industry Management, Political Communication, Media Studies<\\/em><\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":\"1\",\"catid\":2,\"created\":\"2023-04-07 13:32:21\",\"created_by\":189,\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2023-04-07 13:32:21\",\"modified_by\":189,\"checked_out\":null,\"checked_out_time\":null,\"publish_up\":\"2023-04-07 13:32:21\",\"publish_down\":null,\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_image\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_image_alt_txt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_article_format\\\":\\\"standard\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_audio\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_gallery\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_video\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":\"1\",\"ordering\":null,\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":1,\"hits\":0,\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"note\":\"\"}', 0),
(31, 'com_content.article.13', '', '2023-04-07 13:33:08', 189, 3135, 'a6de64428c76678100f38f3f802139e3f9a113a7', '{\"id\":13,\"asset_id\":114,\"title\":\"Ilmu Komunikasi\",\"alias\":\"ilmu-komunikasi\",\"introtext\":\"<p>Wujudkan impian kamu untuk memasuki Kreatif Digital masa kini, di Program Studi:\\u00a0<strong>S1 ILMU KOMUNIKASI\\u00a0<\\/strong>dengan Konsentrasi:<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><img class=\\\"alignnone wp-image-416 size-full\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/infopmb.budiluhur.ac.id\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/09\\/Fikom-Universitas-Budi-Luhur-2020-1.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"903\\\" height=\\\"1280\\\" data-pagespeed-url-hash=\\\"1415837169\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>BROADCAST JOURNALISM (S1 ILMU KOMUNIKASI)<\\/strong><br \\/>News Correspondency, News Presenter\\/Ancor, Reporter, Video Journalist, Media Programming<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>PUBLIC RELATION (S1 ILMU KOMUNIKASI)<\\/strong><br \\/>PR Specialist, Event Planner, Public Diplomacy Officer, PR Digital<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>TOURISM COMMUNICATION (S1 ILMU KOMUNIKASI)<\\/strong><br \\/>Travel Blogger, Travel Vloger, Branding Destination, Tourism Consultant, Travel Content Creator<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>DIGITAL MEDIA &amp; ADVERTISING (S1 ILMU KOMUNIKASI)<\\/strong><br \\/>Brand Manager, Web Content Manager, Social Media Manager, Digital Producer, Media Planner<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><img class=\\\"alignnone wp-image-417 size-full\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/infopmb.budiluhur.ac.id\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/09\\/Fikom-Universitas-Budi-Luhur-2020-3.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"903\\\" height=\\\"1280\\\" loading=\\\"lazy\\\" data-pagespeed-url-hash=\\\"2004837011\\\" \\/><\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":\"1\",\"catid\":2,\"created\":\"2023-04-07 13:33:08\",\"created_by\":189,\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2023-04-07 13:33:08\",\"modified_by\":189,\"checked_out\":null,\"checked_out_time\":null,\"publish_up\":\"2023-04-07 13:33:08\",\"publish_down\":null,\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"ima